article_title: New doctor, Birky, driven to serve diverse cultures
article_text:
Garden City, KS (67846)

Today

Mostly cloudy in the morning with scattered thunderstorms developing later in the day. A few storms may be severe. High 74F. Winds NNW at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 60%..

Tonight

Mostly cloudy skies early, then partly cloudy after midnight. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low 52F. Winds NW at 10 to 20 mph.

article_metadata.author:
ANGIE HAFLICH
ahaflich@gctelegram.com

og.description: For Dr. John Birky, western Kansas’ cultural diversity prompted him to begin his own medical practice in Garden City.
